author: UnclaimedBloom6
changelog: Compatibility for the new secrets system
Score calculator will still be accurate even if not all rooms have been scanned
Legit Mode can now accurately show the user the total number of secrets
Added /rooms <player> and /visited <room> commands to show which rooms a player has been in
Fixed star mob ESP & Wither Door ESP color pickers not working correctly
Your own player head will still show when you are dead
Improved positioning of player icons on the map
Fixed watchdog bot being displayed on the map sometimes
Probably some other stuff I forgot
